title: Rarely Offered -- Sunny Two Bedroom One Bath -- Electricity Included
posting_body: ['Prime Potrero Hill location.', 'On De Haro Street 1/2 block from 23rd Street, which crosses over HWY 101 to SFGH (Zuckerberg SF General Hospital).', 'An easy walk to many of the attractions and conveniences on Potrero Hill, The Mission, and Dogpatch.', 'Access to Highway 101, 280, Caltrain, and Muni minutes away.', 'This large, sunny, and charming Edwardian two-bedroom flat features a floorplan with gorgeous wood floors, etched and stained glass windows, a red vintage tiled kitchen, stainless appliances, and a gas range.', 'Enjoy a meal in the private atrium/light well, or sit on the deck overlooking the beautifully landscaped backyard during the afternoon sun.', 'The large tiled bathroom boasts a 4-foot vanity.', 'Easy street parking.', 'Electricity included (solar-powered property)', 'FREE Washer and Dryer on-site for tenant use', 'Access to unfinished basement with ample storage', "$1000 Security Deposit and last month's rent are required for move in", 'One year lease', 'No smoking', 'Easy show, easy apply', 'Jeff Kremsdorf', 'DRE 01752869']
